01:06:32,146 --> 01:06:33,246
<i>Even if</i>

764
01:06:33,546 --> 01:06:35,316
<i>there's no special reason,</i>

765
01:06:35,316 --> 01:06:36,776
<i>can I see you?</i>

766
01:06:38,246 --> 01:06:39,386
<i>Be careful.</i>

767
01:06:39,386 --> 01:06:42,416
<i>If you get fired because of me,
I can't help you.</i>

768
01:06:42,416 --> 01:06:43,686
<i>Your pictures.</i>

769
01:06:44,016 --> 01:06:45,786
<i>I gave them to Jeong Ah-ran.</i>

770
01:06:45,786 --> 01:06:47,126
<i>You're so high and mighty, huh?</i>

771
01:06:47,126 --> 01:06:50,496
<i>You think I don't have anything on you?</i>

772
01:06:51,226 --> 01:06:53,966
<i>Help me sleep, Jeong-su.</i>

773
01:06:53,966 --> 01:06:55,866
<i>I feel like I'm dying.</i>

774
01:06:56,866 --> 01:06:57,666
<i>Tell me.</i>

775
01:06:57,666 --> 01:06:59,846
<i>What did you two do when I wasn't there?</i>

776
01:06:59,866 --> 01:07:02,036
<i>What could be between those two?</i>

777
01:07:05,046 --> 01:07:06,446
<i>I missed you.</i>

